    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this car to believe it\u2014it\u2019s an absolute gem! It looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've babied this beauty since day one, so it\u2019s in flawless condition and drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for that 'brand new' feel without the brand new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and come take a look!",
