    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 straight-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS timing for razor-sharp power delivery. This example retains its factory-original ZF 6-speed manual gearbox and torque-sensing limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally immaculate with no subframe fatigue, and the suspension bushings remain compliant yet firm for precise turn-in. Finished in flawless original paint with a pristine interior, this vehicle represents a turnkey opportunity for the discerning collector seeking mechanical and aesthetic perfection.",
