    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously preserved since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster, entirely free from swirls, rock chips, or door dings. It has been strictly garage-kept and hand-washed only. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and the original scent remains. Every electronic component, from the crisp infotainment display to the dual-zone climate control, functions flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified technicians. This car drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the lot\u2014featuring tight, responsive suspension, effortless gear transitions, and a whisper-quiet ride. With a clean title and a comprehensive folder of service records included, this is the perfect specimen for a discerning buyer who demands perfection.",
      "price": 44900.0,
